  "title": "Solution Architect",
  "description": "<p>Our client is seeking a Solution Architect to join the Digital Solutions Business Unit, overseeing the design and delivery of enterprise-grade digital solutions for ]customers.</p><ul><li>Lead the solution architecture design for enterprise-grade digital applications</li><li>Ensure compliance with government frameworks, such as GCC, Zero Trust, and IM8, ensuring compatibility and security.</li><li>Work with enterprise software OEMs to design and integrate solutions that are aligned architecture standards.</li><li>Oversee integrations of third-party platforms</li><li>Lead the technical delivery for systems integrations, problem-solving and addressing technical escalations.</li><li>Oversee the technical aspects of solution deployment and go-live, ensuring smooth handover to support teams.</li><li>Act as a technical advisor to stakeholders, ensuring that solutions align with their strategic goals</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Proven leadership in solution architecture, enterprise software delivery, public-sector projects, or digital transformation.</li><li>Experience on systems integration and multi-agency solutions.</li><li>Knowledge of government frameworks, cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP), security standards, and enterprise integration.</li></ul><p>To Apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to: shelly.tan@starcareerconsulting.com<br /></p><p>Shelly Tan Bee Leng (Reg. No. R2199458)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
